  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety of 3 months of Dimebon dosing and the efficacy of Dimebon
      in improving cognitive, motor, and overall function in subjects with Huntington's Disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
